{"tid":810479,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞禁21呎「棺材房」出租","createTime":"2018-09-08T04:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T14:22:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a2ed89bfa978e62cf984a9824b7435baeb284350","tid":810479,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:19:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180908/20494702\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180908%2F20494702&d=9xv0JFbQRmkqdytgjbZEHx4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=e7b211bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180908%2F20494702&h=9c2d1c9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180908/20494702</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月08日 <br />\n<br />\n巴塞禁21呎「棺材房」出租<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180908/large/chris90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180908%2Flarge%2Fchris90.jpg&h=769a260e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「棺材房」不只香港獨有，在房價飛升的西班牙巴塞隆拿亦應運而生，21.5平方呎單位月租200歐元（1,828港元），首批8個單位（圖）原擬本月19日推出，但前日市政府拒發牌，批評單位「不是人住」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市長︰人叠人不合法<br />\n<br />\n蚊型單位「蜂巢」（Haibu）參考日本膠囊酒店設計，長2.2米、高1.2米的空間有單人床、層架式桌子、電視、儲物櫃和插頭位，呎數和月租與香港棺材房相若，稍勝之處是包水電雜費和寬頻網絡費，廚廁和客廳等共用區域每3天有專人打掃。<br />\n<br />\n不過，「蜂巢」只限25至45歲、月入最少450歐元（4,113港元）人士租住，以租不起房子的低收入年輕人為對象，趕絕貧困戶。根據市政府數字，去年巴塞隆拿房子平均月租903歐元（8,254港元），但30歲以下國民平均月入僅1,300歐元（11,880港元），租屋捉襟見肘。<br />\n<br />\n發展商稱單位未推已有500人查詢，但市府拒發牌，市長科洛說：「人叠人是不合法的。」議員埃雷洪道：「墳場也有這樣的住宿，叫做棺材。」發展商辯說：「沒人想住這種房子，但事實月入500歐元的人多的是，若不想露宿街頭，可以考慮。」<br />\n<br />\n法新社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n官員「唱慢板」約束特施政<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n巴西極右總統候選人遇刺重傷"},{"pid":"686fc9f1459c65cb506127e7504a8fc0a5911dc1","tid":810479,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:26:27.000Z","msg":"香港"},{"pid":"07f80528375b2596e107ccb22761e80201e355c3","tid":810479,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:27:52.000Z","msg":"日本"},{"pid":"88b4aa500f79d93583b04966c341d31ec407823b","tid":810479,"uid":20867,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"686fc9f1459c65cb506127e7504a8fc0a5911dc1","tid":810479,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:26:27.000Z","msg":"香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:28:29.000Z","msg":"「不是人住」"},{"pid":"711d979be64edfac33d80b82709ce67e37d525ac","tid":810479,"uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:28:30.000Z","msg":"西班牙平均d人搵咁少錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff5e5275941c630c77f020eec3f27cfe5e7e657","tid":810479,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:29:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2479a5bdf15cb9bd3d7e30f0c1a7ef8840270df","tid":810479,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:29:54.000Z","msg":"如果係香港中位入息2/10人工想有呢個ft. 真係難過登天"},{"pid":"01060c0ed9e056231fe8fe6553dea656937e9c59","tid":810479,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"711d979be64edfac33d80b82709ce67e37d525ac","tid":810479,"uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:28:30.000Z","msg":"西班牙平均d人搵咁少錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:30:04.000Z","msg":"窮得有骨氣   訓街唔訓棺材"},{"pid":"1d55cd66ada76092f9074bb3fcbb7646e917e872","tid":810479,"uid":133450,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:31:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">議員埃雷洪道：「墳場也有這樣的住宿，叫做棺材。」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afdf241dc56437eda4ec2b35f2a583a52ee1fc9c","tid